name: Random growth (recovery of all things)
description:
The chain is the random growth of grass and wood in spring. The random superposition of circular pictures will have a different effect
Before obtaining this token, you must understand that it has 6 functions

--Background theme
--Chain orientation
--Light source
--Circular size
--Circular color
--Chain random number

The token has six characteristics: quality, time, minimum growth, maximum growth, and attribute
If you want to save the picture, press and hold tab + enter or click the left mouse button to save the JPG picture
